                "nuclide": "26-FE-54",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.96
              },
              "free_text": [
                " F-82H alloy composition is 7.1Cr-",
                "1.8W-0.55Si-0.40Mn-0.17V-0.1C-0.04Ta. 54Fe in the",
                "alloy compromised  96% of the iron or 86% of the total",
                "alloy by weight."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
